                     <note type="content-genre">Kalām (Islamic Scholastic Theology)</note>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_3034">Irshād al-muz̤illīn fī is̱bāt nubuvvah khātam al-nabīyīn</title>
